<PB N="26">
<HEAD><MILESTONE N="26a" UNIT="folio">THE SPHERES AND PLANETS.</HEAD>
<P>&para; Philosofirs puttyn 9 speris vndirewritten; but Diuinis puttin &thorn;e ten&thorn;e|spere, where is heuyn empire, in &thorn;e whiche, angelis &amp; sowlis<NOTE PLACE="foot">lis is the MS. l with a line at right angles to it.</NOTE> of|seyntis seruen god; in &thorn;e whiche is crist, in &thorn;e same forme that he|walkid in er&thorn;e, and also owre lady, &amp; seyntis that arosen with criste.</P>
<P>&para; &THORN;e first spere of &thorn;e 9 is clepid 'primum mobile,' &thorn;e first mevabil thyng.</P>
<P>&para; &THORN;e .ij. spere of sterris: Aries .1. &thorn;e rame.  &para; the secund hows of Mars,|&thorn;e bool, &para; &thorn;e secund hows of Venus, Gemini, &para; &thorn;e secund hows of|Mercuri, Cancer.  &para; &thorn;e hows of &thorn;e mone, leo. &thorn;e hows of &thorn;e sonne,|Virgo. // &thorn;e first hows of Mercury, Libra // &thorn;e first hows of Venus,|Scorpio // &thorn;e first hows of Mars, Sagittarius // &thorn;e first hows of Iubiter,|Capricornus // &thorn;e first hows of Saturne, Aquarius // &thorn;e secund hows of|Saturne, Piscis./ &thorn;e secunde hows of Iubiter [<I>no more</I>].</P>
<P>&para; Saturn is a planete evel-willid and ful of sekenes.  Wherfore he is|peyntid with an hooke, for he repe&thorn; down grene thyngis / he fulfilli&thorn;|his course in xxx &yogh;eere.</P>
<P>&para; Iubiter is a planete wele willyng to alle thingis to be gendrid, plent[i]ful|&amp; plesyng; therfor he is y-seid Iubiter as helpyn. in xij [&yogh;]eere he|filli&thorn; his course.</P>
<P>&para; Mars is an enemy to alle thyngis to be gendrid; wherfor he is clepid|god of batel, for he is ful of tempest. he fulfilli&thorn; his course in .ij.|&yogh;eere.</P>
<P><MILESTONE N="26b" UNIT="folio">&para; &THORN;e sonne is &thorn;e worthiest planet, y-set in myddis. he fulfilli&thorn; his course in|CCClxv dayes &amp; vj. howris, &thorn;e whiche causen bisext.</P>
<P>&para; Venus is apte to alle thyngis to be gendrid. he fulfilli&thorn; his course in|CCCxxxvj daies.</P>
<P>&para; Mercuri swyft is y-seid a messenger of daies [? heuene]. he fulfilli&thorn; his|course in CCCxxxvj daies.</P>
<P>&para; &THORN;e mone is a planete ny &thorn;e er&thorn;e.  [<I>ends.</I>]</P></DIV2></DIV1>
